DOC.brief_summary: The objective of the study is to investigate the relative bioavailability of digoxin after concomitant multiple oral administration of BI 10773 and a single dose of digoxin in comparison to digoxin given alone to healthy male and female subjects.
DOC.brief_title: Drug Interaction Study of Digoxin and BI 10773
DOC.criteria: Inclusion criteria: Healthy male and female subjects Exclusion criteria: Any relevant deviation from healthy conditions
